Been doodling a lot recently. I&#039;ve also recently got a Wacom Tablet so been practicing on that. Been recently drawing a bunch of Gnar stuff, but theres one part about him that I&#039;m unfamiliar with. I&#039;ve seen all different kinds of Gnar fan art and there&#039;s always a split. Is the brown stuff around Gnar&#039;s upper chest/neck brown fur or a bunch of leaves/vegetation? With all the art I see, its either one or the other. The texturing on the 3D model kind of looks like fur, but I&#039;m not too sure... I&#039;d like to know what it really is. 

Riot or anyone who knows... halp?

